    "title": {
      "rendered": "10 Online Job Boards for Nonprofit Professionals"
    },
    "content": {
      "rendered": "<p><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/10-Online-Job-Boards-for-Nonprofit-Professionals-Square.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-19656\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-19656\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/10-Online-Job-Boards-for-Nonprofit-Professionals-Square-300x300.jpg?resize=300%2C300\" alt=\"10 Online Job Boards for Nonprofit Professionals Square\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/10-Online-Job-Boards-for-Nonprofit-Professionals-Square.jpg?resize=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/10-Online-Job-Boards-for-Nonprofit-Professionals-Square.jpg?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/10-Online-Job-Boards-for-Nonprofit-Professionals-Square.jpg?resize=200%2C200&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/10-Online-Job-Boards-for-Nonprofit-Professionals-Square.jpg?resize=75%2C75&amp;ssl=1 75w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/10-Online-Job-Boards-for-Nonprofit-Professionals-Square.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a>If you are a nonprofit professional feeling restless or unsatisfied at your current job, 2016 is shaping up to be a good year to make a change. According to the <strong><a href=\"http://www.nonprofithr.com/education-insights/research-data/\" target=\"_blank\">2016 Nonprofit Employment Practices Report</a></strong>, 57% of nonprofits plan on creating new positions in 2016. The greatest growth is expected in the area of fundraising (44%). Skills in marketing and communications are also in high demand (37%). When applying for jobs in the nonprofit sector, here are <strong><a href=\"http://nonprofitwithballs.com/2016/04/hey-job-applicants-stop-doing-these-dumbass-things/\" target=\"_blank\">40 mistakes to avoid making</a>\u00a0</strong>and if you are an employer, here are <strong><a href=\"http://nonprofitwithballs.com/2016/04/hey-can-we-be-a-little-nicer-to-job-applicants-and-stop-treating-them-like-crap/\" target=\"_blank\">20 ways you can make the hiring process easier</a></strong> for yourself and prospective employees.</p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">1. Idealist<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.idealist.org/\" target=\"_blank\">idealist.org</a>\u00a0\u2605\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/IdealistCareers\" target=\"_blank\">@idealistcareers</a></h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.idealist.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-19629\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-19629\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/idealist.png?resize=600%2C289\" alt=\"idealist\" width=\"600\" height=\"289\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/idealist.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/idealist.png?resize=300%2C145&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">\u00a02.\u00a0Work for Good<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.workforgood.org/\" target=\"_blank\">workforgood.org</a>\u00a0\u2605\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/workforgoodorg\" target=\"_blank\">@workforgoodorg</a></h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.workforgood.org/\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-20744\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/Work-for-Good.png?resize=600%2C332\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"332\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/Work-for-Good.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/Work-for-Good.png?resize=300%2C166&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">3. The Bridgespan Group<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bridgespan.org/Services-and-Expertise/Services/Nonprofit-Job-Board.aspx\" target=\"_blank\">bridgespan.org</a>\u00a0\u2605\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/bridgespangroup\" target=\"_blank\">@bridgespangroup</a></h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.bridgespan.org/Services-and-Expertise/Services/Nonprofit-Job-Board.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-19640\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-19640\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/bridgespan.png?resize=600%2C339\" alt=\"bridgespan\" width=\"600\" height=\"339\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/bridgespan.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/bridgespan.png?resize=300%2C170&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">4. Philanthropy News Digest<br />\n<a href=\"http://philanthropynewsdigest.org/jobs\" target=\"_blank\">philanthropynewsdigest.org</a>\u00a0\u2605\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/pndblog\" target=\"_blank\">@pndblog</a></h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://philanthropynewsdigest.org/jobs\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-19645\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-19645\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/philanthropynewsdigest.png?resize=600%2C313\" alt=\"philanthropynewsdigest\" width=\"600\" height=\"313\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/philanthropynewsdigest.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/philanthropynewsdigest.png?resize=300%2C157&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">5. Chronicle of Philanthropy<br />\n<a href=\"https://philanthropy.com/jobs?cid=UCOPNAVTOP\" target=\"_blank\">philanthropy.com</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/philanthropy\" target=\"_blank\">@philanthropy</a></h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://philanthropy.com/jobs?cid=UCOPNAVTOP\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-19643\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-19643\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/philanthropy.png?resize=600%2C298\" alt=\"philanthropy\" width=\"600\" height=\"298\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/philanthropy.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/philanthropy.png?resize=300%2C149&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">6. Charity Village (Canada)<br />\n<a href=\"http://charityvillage.com/\" target=\"_blank\">charityvillage.com</a>\u00a0\u2605\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/charityvillage\" target=\"_blank\">@charityvillage</a></h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://charityvillage.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-19637\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-19637\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/charityvillage.png?resize=600%2C288\" alt=\"charityvillage\" width=\"600\" height=\"288\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/charityvillage.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/charityvillage.png?resize=300%2C144&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">7. Third Sector Jobs (UK)<br />\n<a href=\"http://jobs.thirdsector.co.uk/\" target=\"_blank\">jobs.thirdsector.co.uk</a>\u00a0\u2605\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/jobsthirdsector\" target=\"_blank\">@jobsthirdsector</a></h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://jobs.thirdsector.co.uk\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-19649\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-19649\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/third-sector-jobs.png?resize=600%2C292\" alt=\"third sector jobs\" width=\"600\" height=\"292\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/third-sector-jobs.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/third-sector-jobs.png?resize=300%2C146&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">9. Pro Bono Australia<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.probonoaustralia.com.au/\" target=\"_blank\">probonoaustralia.com.au</a>\u00a0\u2605\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ProBonoNews/\" target=\"_blank\">@probononews</a></h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://probonoaustralia.com.au/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-19652\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-19652\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/probono-australia.png?resize=600%2C279\" alt=\"probono australia\" width=\"600\" height=\"279\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/probono-australia.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/probono-australia.png?resize=300%2C140&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">9. DevNetJobs.org (International)<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.devnetjobs.org/\" target=\"_blank\">devnetjobs.org</a>\u00a0\u2605\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/devnetjobs\" target=\"_blank\">@devnetjobs</a></h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.devnetjobs.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-19647\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-19647\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/devnetjobs.png?resize=600%2C349\" alt=\"devnetjobs\" width=\"600\" height=\"349\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/devnetjobs.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/devnetjobs.png?resize=300%2C175&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">10. United Nations Jobs (International)<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.unjobs.org/\" target=\"_blank\">unjobs.org</a>\u00a0\u2014 <a href=\"https://twitter.com/UNjobs\" target=\"_blank\">@UNjobs</a></h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.unjobs.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-19653\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-19653\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/UN-JOBS.png?resize=600%2C288\" alt=\"UN JOBS\" width=\"600\" height=\"288\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/UN-JOBS.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/UN-JOBS.png?resize=300%2C144&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<hr />\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold;\"><em>Mobile for Good: A How-To Fundraising Guide for Nonprofits</em></span></span></strong></h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Mobile-Good-How--Fundraising-Nonprofits/dp/0071825460\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignleft wp-image-16024\" style=\"margin: 10px; border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/mobile-for-good-look-inside.jpg?resize=99%2C150\" alt=\"mobile for good look inside\" width=\"99\" height=\"150\" /></a>Based on more than 20 years of experience and 25,000+ hours spent utilizing mobile and social media, <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Mobile-Good-How--Fundraising-Nonprofits/dp/0071825460\" target=\"_blank\"><em><strong>Mobile for Good: A How-To Fundraising Guide for Nonprofits</strong></em></a> is a comprehensive 256-page book packed with more than 500 best practices. Written on the premise that all communications and fundraising are now mobile and social, Mobile for Good is a step-by-step how-to guide for writing, implementing, and maintaining a mobile and social fundraising strategy for your nonprofit.</p>\n",
